reviews.review_text:
the sound of tripping We can argue whether the band peaked in '69 or '72, or anywhere in between, but this show is the real deal.

I haven't tripped in years (decades), but the reprise of Cryptical reminds me of it.

This is an excellent soundboard. I'm only up to Black Peter, but I'm going to start my other machine downloading and burning this show immediately. I suggest you do the same.
I Thought I Heard..... Is It The Ringing In My Ears Or Is There A Banjo And Possibly A Mandolin In Uncle John's Band ?
